					<p>New deadline: 15 March 2012For more information please contact:African Crop Science Journal Secretariat Makerere UniversityCollege of Agricultural and Environmental Sciences P.O. Box 7062, Kampala, UgandaTel. + 256 772 478404; +256 772 468 919&nbsp;Email: jstenywa@agric.mak.ac.ug; nampalap@agric.mak.ac.ug; acsjclimatechange@gmail.com; acss@agric.mak.ac.ug</p>
