					<p>http://www.hks.harvard.edu/centers/cid/programs/sustsci/grants-fellowships/fellows/fellowships-in-sustainability-science<b>Deadline: 15 January 2012</b>The Sustainability Science Fellowships are open to advanced doctoral and post-doctoral students, and to mid-career professionals engaged in research or practice in sustainable science. The Sustainability Science Program aims to facilitate the design, implementation, and evaluation of effective interventions that promote sustainable development.</p>
