						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Fellowships-grants-calls/PhD-student-Ecosystem-Service-Modelling-in-Western-Africa-WUR-AfricaRice" title="PhD student ‘Ecosystem Service Modelling in Western Africa’ (WUR, AfricaRice)" alt="link">PhD student ‘Ecosystem Service Modelling in Western Africa’ (WUR, AfricaRice)</a></h2>

	
					<p>The PhD student has to undertake a spatial modeling of ecosystem services supply in the context of land degradation and intensification processes with a case study in Western Africa (Benin or Mali). The project will combine environmental, spatial and economic analysis to further our understanding of the benefits provided by various ecosystems to society. The project will be undertaken in close collaboration with the Africa Rice Center in Benin. The PhD student is expected to spend around 50% of the time for this research project in either Benin or Mali.<a href="http://www.academictransfer.com/employer/WUR/vacancy/11870/lang/en/" target="_blank">http://www.academictransfer.com/employer/WUR/vacancy/11870/lang/en/</a><b>Deadline for applications is 1 December 2011 or until the vacancy is filled.</b></p>
							<p><span class="date">9/11/2011</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Fellowships-grants-calls/PhD-student-Ecosystem-Service-Modelling-in-Western-Africa-WUR-AfricaRice">Read more...</a>
