<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/CTA-and-S-T/Fellowships-grants-calls/Fellowships-International-Centre-for-Trade-and-Sustainable-development" title="Fellowships – International Centre for Trade and Sustainable development" alt="link">Fellowships – International Centre for Trade and Sustainable development</a></h2>

	
					<p>Deadline: 31 December 2011ICTSD Fellowships are awarded through a competitive selection process. Eminent policy experts, academics, scholars, and others with a deep interest in trade and sustainable development policy research, debate and implementation from any region of the world are invited to apply. Applications for Fellowship can be submitted by 01 October and 01 February of each year, and if successful, a candidate is given a two year appointment that is open to renewal. Further information is provided <a href="http://ictsd.org/i/jobs/113725/" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>
							<p><span class="date">2/11/2011</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
